          <p class='first-para'>
            If we go on like this, we are breaking the law. We are denigrating people. It will go into <span class="italic">Hansard</span> and be published. It is actionable.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0651P0-04418'>
