            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_202gc' title='Col. 202GC &mdash; HL Deb 14 July 2003 vol 651 c202GC' name='column_202gc' href='#column_202gc' rel='bookmark'>202GC</a>
            is the simplest way in which to do this. This is very mild, and I would suppose that the Government would say&#x2014;I certainly hope they will&#x2014;that once again they intend that this shall be the case, and because they intend it to be the case, it will be the case.</p><p>
